OL,7,FVictims may be asked to call their
OL,8,Fbank using the phone number on the
OL,9,Fback of their card, or to hang up and
OL,10,Fcall 101 or 999 to verify an officer's
OL,11,Fidentity. This convinces you that the
OL,12,Fcall is genuine, but the scammer has
OL,13,Fkept the line open at their end, so
OL,14,Fwhen the call is made, you are
OL,15,Funknowingly connected straight back to
OL,16,Fthem or their friends.
